videos.title: Mythic Sultai Wrath, Token Army Warrior and More!  Tarkir Dragonstorm MTG Spoilers
videos.description:
We wrap up the first week of Magic: the Gathering's Tarkir: Dragonstorm spoilers with a wild mythic wrath, a three-drop that can make a ton of tokens, one of the best blink and Panharmonicon creatures ever and so much more! Let's discuss!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

More spoilers: https://www.mtgpreviews.com
